The paper deals with computer vision approaches for plant disease detection, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models for classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of internet scraped images, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the use of models to increase classification accuracy, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
